By":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"有無人睇過本書叫順豐王朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n評價點 想買"},{"pid":"f7dfcba676f42487b8aedc201ff4e6a182246205","tid":133980,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:31:09.000Z","msg":"以前係好多香港人運水貨<br />\n<br />\n其實運水貨有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3972d3996abebef53f830b487bbc4995e54c3d2f","tid":133980,"uid":3735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"命黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d88b4c30704e8351b4990072bac19a284b18bfbc","tid":133980,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:39:11.000Z","msg":"香港本業係物流嘛<br />\n做物流梗有得發格<br />\n之前睇貿發局，香港有幾百間「物流」，大部分得幾個至十幾個員工<br />\n問題係依家啲走水貨係行係街上面，阻民生看係問題之嘛<br />\n係咪唔記得佢地點搶奶粉？"},{"pid":"7778940dca229b05371a4a7a87563d104b12f874","tid":133980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:40:11.000Z","msg":"走私起家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2c65a1e9a1b221deffe190dabb07a8b42d05d2","tid":133980,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"間公司話誠實係用人原則，轉個頭要人作假地址昆大陸海關，佢俾份list 等個客走咗自行幫個客填"},{"pid":"a8f920ee73f09149d804a6f88a60ca7e7f9ad58b","tid":133980,"uid":32650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"個陣佢岩岩開始個陣好撚愁 <br />\n<br />\n企係羅湖關口幫人每袋貨十幾廿蚊 運去山卡拉地方 <br />\n<br />\n佢醒目 個陣係關口搵返當地鄉下既丫婆做腳"},{"pid":"d58e465ae408e1eb4659c333e1f34f66c823bda2","tid":133980,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間公司話誠實係用人原則，轉個頭要人作假地址昆大陸海關，佢俾份list 等個客走咗自行幫個客填</blockquote><br />